description:
Deadly Forest is a Game where your first objective is to stay alive as long you can.
To gather more points you need to increase the multiplier value. for this you have more options:
- every time you start a new race you have a multiplier determined by your previous races, for coins and distance;
- after every 100 coins collected, coins multiplier increase for that race;
- after every 250 m, distance multiplier increase only for that race;
- for increasing your starting multiplier you have to collect at least 500 coins or run more than 500 m.

I recommend this game to install on devices with at least: 
- RAM 512 Mb or more;
-CPU single core 1 GHz or higher.

