Eating up the fruits the snake is growing. Control your snake, eat fruites, keep off the walls and do not bite yourself!

The main characteristics of game:
- Exemplary gameplay: only snake, apples and movement;
- Different types of control: you can always choose the best for you;
- Modern interface, possibly the best among Snakes for Android;
- Local and global table of records, the possibility to share your results with friends.

We realized the classic game process of first snakes from tetris and first Nokias, when only snake and it's target are on the field. 
The possibility to choose different variants of control in settings is one of the advantage of our snake:
* 4 buttons - each button sets the direction for movement;
* 2 buttons - for turning on the left/on the right from the current direction;
* swypes - you should swipe your finger to set a new moving direction for snake;
* gyroscope - turn your device to set new direction.

The game is based on the latest version of one of the best game engines Unity3D. That provides high quality and correct drawing on any device. The basis of our interface are pictures which were made by our painter in detail. And the realization passed through the hands of a vigilant person who was responsible for usability testing. The screenshots can show better than a hundred words. 
There are two tables of records: local - where you can see 10 best results, gathered on one device, and global - showing the best results all over the world. Notable that the game asks for the name of player, in order you can give to play your friend, and he can save the record by his name. Also you can share any result through sms, e-mail or any social network, that used on your smartphone - twitter, facebook, vkontakte, etc.

The main idea is to follow the simple advice - 'do not bite yourself', and luck befriends you for sure.

